    <string name="about1">I-Zazen Meditation Timer - Isibali-sikhathi esilula sokuzindla esinezigaba ezenziwe ngokwezifiso, imisindo yensimbi, nokuphathwa kweseshini.</string>
    <string name="about2">Idalwe nguStefan Gaffga. Okwamanje inakekelwa u-Georg Graf.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Siyabonga ku-Winfried we-&lt;a href="http://www.meditationsuhren.de"&gt;http://www.meditationsuhren.de&lt;/a&gt; ngokuhlinzeka ngemisindo ye-Bell emihle kangaka!</string>
    <string name="about3">&lt;a href="https://github.com/georgernstgraf/zazentimer/issues"&gt;Bika izinkinga ku-GitHub&lt;/a&gt;</string>
    <string name="app_description">Lolu hlelo lokusebenza luvumela umsebenzisi ukuthi achaze isethi yezikhathi zokuzindla futhi lunikeze isibali sikhathi ngempendulo ebonakalayo nezwakalayo uma ingxenye noma ukuzindla konke sekuphelile.</string>
