    <string name="help_sectionlist_text">Lapha ungakwazi ukusho, ukuchaza futhi uhlele okuqukethwe kweSeshini yakho.\n\nUKUHLELWA KABUSHA\nUkuze uhlele kabusha izinto, cindezela isikhathi eside entweni futhi\nidonsele endaweni yayo entsha.\n\nUKUSUSA\nUkuze ususe into, yihambise kwesokudla.\n\nHLELA\nUkuze uhlele isigaba, vele usithinte kanye.\n\nENGEZA\nUkwengeza isigaba esisha, cindezela inkinobho ethi +.</string>
